title: Game Ka Na Ba?
overview: Game Ka Na Ba?, formerly Pilipinas Game Ka Na Ba? (stylized as Game KNB?) is a Philippine game show created by ABS-CBN. The main goal of the game is to win the jackpot by successfully answering multiple trivia questions.The show was revived on October 12, 2020, on Jeepney TV, with a brand new format wherein anyone around the world may join via the Kumu app. After five questions, the remaining players split the prize among themselves.
